messages.content:
I'll help you with that mediacontrol request.

<action>
{
  "intent": "MediaControl",
  "entities": {
    "action": "play",
    "room": "bedroom",
    "device": "tv"
  }
}
</action>

Turning off the bedroom lights

<action>
{
  "intent": "TurnOffLight",
  "entities": {
    "room": "bedroom",
    "device": "lights"
  }
}
</action>

The bedroom is now off.

Turning off the {room} lights

<action>
{
  "intent": "TurnOffLight",
  "entities": {
    "group": "all",
    "device": "lights"
  }
}
</action>

The all is now off.

Turning on the kitchen {device}

<action>
{
  "intent": "TurnOnLight",
  "entities": {
    "room": "kitchen"
  }
}
</action>

The kitchen is now on.

Here's the view from front door

<action>
{
  "intent": "ShowCamera",
  "entities": {
    "location": "front door",
    "device": "camera"
  }
}
</action>

The front door is now unlocked

<action>
{
  "intent": "UnlockDoor",
  "entities": {
    "door": "front door"
  }
}
</action>

The door has been unlocked.

I'll help you with that turnonswitch request.

<action>
{
  "intent": "TurnOnSwitch",
  "entities": {
    "room": "living room",
    "device": "fan"
  }
}
</action>

The living room is now on.

Unlocking the front door

<action>
{
  "intent": "UnlockDoor",
  "entities": {
    "door": "front door"
  }
}
</action>

The door has been unlocked.

I'll help you with that mediacontrol request.

<action>
{
  "intent": "MediaControl",
  "entities": {
    "action": "play",
    "room": "bedroom",
    "device": "tv"
  }
}
</action>

I'll help you with that mediacontrol request.

<action>
{
  "intent": "MediaControl",
  "entities": {
    "action": "pause",
    "room": "living room",
    "device": "tv"
  }
}
</action>

I'll help you with that turnonswitch request.

<action>
{
  "intent": "TurnOnSwitch",
  "entities": {
    "location": "patio left",
    "device": "outlet"
  }
}
</action>

The patio left is now on.

bedroom lights brightness is now at 50%

<action>
{
  "intent": "DimLight",
  "entities": {
    "room": "bedroom",
    "device": "lights",
    "brightness": "50"
  }
}
</action>

Setting living room {device} to 30 percent

<action>
{
  "intent": "DimLight",
  "entities": {
    "room": "living room",
    "brightness": "30"
  }
}
</action>

Turning off the bedroom lights

<action>
{
  "intent": "TurnOffLight",
  "entities": {
    "room": "bedroom",
    "device": "lights"
  }
}
</action>

The bedroom is now off.

I'll help you with that activatescene request.

<action>
{
  "intent": "ActivateScene",
  "entities": {
    "room": "bedroom",
    "scene": "relax"
  }
}
</action>
